<br>
Sit aggro is somewhere under 1200 aggro (as I can taunt, proc 1 EB and a caster can always sit outside melee range).<br>
<br>
Proximatey aggro I would also estimate to be around 500 hate (+500 hate to anyone in melee range).<br>
<br>
Have a wizzie pull a mob with a DD.  When mob gets to wizzie, immediately AE taunt it off him without attacking.  Have wizzie immediately cast another small nuke.  If the mob aggros wizzie then the hate from AE taunt is less than the nuke value.<br>
<br>
You have to do it all prety quickly as hate does decay (hate decreases with time).<br>
<br>
I did this back in early/mid luclin to get my opinion on the matter.<br>
